---
title: All-American Crumbed Chicken & Cheesy Potatoes with Pea Pod Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: You simply can't go wrong with crumbed chicken, roasted 'taters and a creamy smokey aioli to tie a meal together; and with only four steps, this easy dinner will be ready in a flash!

